Package stocker.model.general

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BollingerBands
    The class class BollingerBands defines the indicator “Bollinger Bands”.
    DataProviderProfile
    Stores the data used to connect to a data provider
    FrameProfile
    The frame profiles are used to contain data about all the different gui frames i.e. size, position.
    FrameProfileBase
    This defines the base of the frame profiles
    FrameProfileChart
    The chart frame profiles are used to contain data about gui frames and additional chart frame data i.e. symbol and indicators.
    IndicatorBase
    This abstract class is a basis of the indicators.
    SimpleMovingAverage
    The SimpleMovingAverage class defines the “Simple Moving Average” indicator.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChartType
    The chart type determines how the chart will be shown or rendered.
    DisplayType
    The display type determines "where" the data will be shown or rendered.
    IndicatorType
    Enum to name and identify an indicator
    TimeInterval
    The time interval determines the resolution and the time window of the considered stock data
    ViewType
    The frame type determines the type of view
